  <refsect1>
    <title>DESCRIPTION</title>

    <para>The &geamd; is a <abbrev>SMTP</abbrev> proxy which is able to encrypt
      or decrypt mail on the fly. It is not a full MTA as it depends
      on smarthosts for routing.</para>

  </refsect1>


&geamdoptions;

